<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>The last post is correct.  You get the staff and something that has unlimited charges of identify.  However, the one in oasis is not as stated before.  I invised myself and swam down in between 2 goblins and grabbed it, then swam away, no problem.  The one I found to be very tough, unless you know exactly where the rod is, is the one in Erud's Crossing.  There are Killer Sharks down there, three of them and they are something like level 40-45 and see invis.  I suggest going to graffe.com and check out their spoiler and walkthru to find out the exact location of this rod so you can swim down and get it.  I was level 20 when I first tried to get this rod.  When I finally got it I was level 18.</font></td></tr></table>
